  "title": "BIM Modeller cum Drafter",
  "description": "<p><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for all drafting and preparation of drawings on time for all projects</li>\n  <li>Develop and manage 3D building models using BIM software</li>\n  <li>Produce BIM model deliverables for design, documentation and fabrication purpose</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance of drawing with regulatory specification</li>\n  <li>Work closely with project teams on drawing amendments and updated</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess at least Diploma/Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Required language(s): English</li>\n  <li>At least 1 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li>\n  <li>Prior experience with<strong> Fire Prevention &amp; Protection Systems </strong>will be added advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please <strong>indicate the below information in your resume</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Employment experience</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected Salary</li>\n  <li>Reason(s) for leaving</li>\n  <li>Availability to commerce work</li>\n</ul>",
